snippet.title: Baldimore's Highschool - Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
He's back.

You wake up in your high school at night. You have no memory of how you got there. All the doors are locked. You hear footsteps and a faint slapping sound. Something's wrong... Find a way to escape the school or try to survive the night. Collect various items and uncover the secret of Baldi's high school.

Features:

- 5 Different Endings

- Either play the game stealthily and sneak your way out or fight your way out using various items

- Music by Jonathan Watkins

Available on Itch io and Game Jolt! 

Itch io - https://endless-code.itch.io/baldimores-highschool

Game Jolt - https://gamejolt.com/games/baldimores-highschool/349768
